snippet.title: For Janardhana Reddy's Big Wedding, Money Laundered, Claims Suicide Note

localized.description: Mining baron and former minister Janardhana Reddy  laundered 100 crores of untaxed money ahead of his daughter's internationally-headlined wedding last month,  a driver in Karnataka has alleged in a note left behind after he killed himself yesterday.
